{"tid":916803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張智霖袁詠儀區瑞強都撐陳凱欣 網民：罷買FANCL","createTime":"2018-11-26T03:02:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T14:57:03.000Z","uid":42565,"like":32,"dislike":147,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"e307e11dc6f7a4363baea9343d9a512938c5a3e3","tid":916803,"uid":42565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T03:02:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181126/large/1543186290_c786.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181126%2Flarge%2F1543186290_c786.png&h=85857b09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n地區零政績、空降九西首次競逐立法會議員之位的陳凱欣，以106,457票勝出今次補選，得票更多於李卓人和馮檢基的總和。除前食衞局長高永文等多位建制派名人為陳助選外，部分演藝人亦為陳站台，不但有在造勢會亮相的「肥媽」Maria Cordero，中聯辦旗下的網媒《橙新聞》亦在facebook刊登相片指，人稱「Cool魔」的張智霖及其妻袁詠儀、區瑞強等，昨午都到投票站支持陳凱欣。﻿有網民轉載照片時，直言會罷買由張智霖代言的護膚品牌FANCL。<br />\n<br />\n網民點睇<br />\nEdward Kwong：出得嚟行，遲早要還<br />\nKenneth Wong：班偽人原來又係建制狗<br />\nEdmund Chiu：原來兩公婆都趕住做畜牲，賤X格<br />\nJenny Wu：是非不分的偽人"},{"pid":"374038ac6b39469e070e5032dce629822a053803","tid":916803,"uid":16844,"like":107,"dislike":3,"score":104,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T03:07:37.000Z","msg":"唔買fancl了"},{"pid":"b7dd44db2959406cc0a8e4135165716c2784f749","tid":916803,"uid":209097,"like":102,"dislike":8,"score":94,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T03:08:38.000Z","msg":"都話左香港人同支那人無分別架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11f34535d2393c966c5b64ce59311fc3ede6ff9","tid":916803,"uid":66839,"like":3,"dislike":47,"score":-44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T03:08:46.000Z","msg":"搵食者， 犯法啊"},{"pid":"472c94dc06bf773f578807b19cfe5ffd15900223","tid":916803,"uid":79563,"like":142,"dislike":8,"score":134,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T03:08:56.000Z","msg":"港豬既罷買就收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n講罷買, 支那狗仲團結過港豬"},{"pid":"4ddf07b607a40c24406e3b3ee9d3dceabacb6995","tid":916803,"uid":2772,"like":49,"dislike":2,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T03:09:06.000Z","msg":"一